					<p class="ing-extra">• ANTISEPTIC PROPERTIES TO PREVENT BREAKOUTS.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="mobile-modal" id="modal-rooibos">
			<div class="modal-box">
				<button class="modal-x" data-close="modal-rooibos">✕</button>
				<h3>INGREDIENTS</h3>
				<p>NATURAL TALLOW, PALM OIL, COCONUT OIL, ESSENTIAL OILS, NATURAL CLAYS, EXFOLIATING SEEDS, ROOIBOS, TEA TREE</p>
				<hr/>
				<p class="bullet-item">RICH IN ANTIOXIDANTS FOR CELLULAR REPAIR.</p>
				<p class="bullet-item">ANTI-INFLAMMATORY HELPS SOOTHE ECZEMA.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Cocoa Coconut -->
		<section class="page-section product-biome" id="cocoa">
			<div class="nature-bg" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920');"></div>
			<div class="section-content product-layout">
				<div class="side-panel desktop-only">
					<p class="bullet-item">COCONUT OIL DEEPLY MOISTURIZES SKIN.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">ANTIBACTERIAL PROPERTIES FIGHT ACNE.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">CACAO PACKED WITH ANTIOXIDANTS FOR GLOW.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">IMPROVES ELASTICITY AND MICRO-CIRCULATION.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="main-interaction">
					<img src="/cocoa_hero.png" alt="Cocoa Coconut" class="product-pure-img" />
					<h2 class="main-title">Cocoa Coconut</h2>
					<p class="main-price">R100</p>
					<div class="buying-tools">
						<div class="quantity-box">
							<button class="qty-dec" data-pid="cocoa">-</button>
							<span class="qty-count" id="qty-val-cocoa">1</span>
							<button class="qty-inc" data-pid="cocoa">+</button>
						</div>
						<button class="add-btn" data-name="Cocoa Coconut" data-pid="cocoa">
							<span class="add-label">ADD TO ORDER</span>
							<span class="add-ok">✓ ADDED</span>
						</button>
					</div>
					<button class="ing-open mobile-only" data-modal="modal-cocoa">SEE INGREDIENTS</button>
				</div>
				<div class="side-panel desktop-only">
					<h3 class="ing-title">INGREDIENTS</h3>
					<p class="ing-text">NATURAL TALLOW, PALM OIL, COCONUT OIL, ESSENTIAL OILS, NATURAL CLAYS, EXFOLIATING SEEDS, COCOA, COCONUT</p>
					<p class="ing-extra">• INTENSE HYDRATION FOR DRY SKIN.</p>
					<p class="ing-extra">• PROMOTES A YOUTHFUL, FIRM APPEARANCE.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="mobile-modal" id="modal-cocoa">
			<div class="modal-box">
				<button class="modal-x" data-close="modal-cocoa">✕</button>
				<h3>INGREDIENTS</h3>
				<p>NATURAL TALLOW, PALM OIL, COCONUT OIL, ESSENTIAL OILS, NATURAL CLAYS, EXFOLIATING SEEDS, COCOA, COCONUT</p>
				<hr/>
				<p class="bullet-item">COCONUT OIL DEEPLY MOISTURIZES SKIN.</p>
				<p class="bullet-item">CACAO PACKED WITH ANTIOXIDANTS FOR GLOW.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Rainforest Herbs -->
		<section class="page-section product-biome" id="rainforest">
			<div class="nature-bg" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920');"></div>
			<div class="section-content product-layout">
				<div class="side-panel desktop-only">
					<p class="bullet-item">TALLOW IS BIO-IDENTICAL TO SEBUM.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">RICH IN VITAMINS A, D, E, AND K.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">MIXED HERBS PROVIDE BOTANICAL ANTIOXIDANTS.</p>
					<p class="bullet-item">NATURAL CLEANSING WITHOUT STRIPPING OILS.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="main-interaction">
					<img src="/rainforest_hero.png" alt="Rainforest Herbs" class="product-pure-img" />
					<h2 class="main-title">Rainforest Herbs</h2>
					<p class="main-price">R100</p>
					<div class="buying-tools">
						<div class="quantity-box">
							<button class="qty-dec" data-pid="rainforest">-</button>
							<span class="qty-count" id="qty-val-rainforest">1</span>
							<button class="qty-inc" data-pid="rainforest">+</button>
						</div>
						<button class="add-btn" data-name="Rainforest Herbs" data-pid="rainforest">
							<span class="add-label">ADD TO ORDER</span>
							<span class="add-ok">✓ ADDED</span>
						</button>
					</div>
					<button class="ing-open mobile-only" data-modal="modal-rainforest">SEE INGREDIENTS</button>
				</div>
				<div class="side-panel desktop-only">
					<h3 class="ing-title">INGREDIENTS</h3>
					<p class="ing-text">NATURAL TALLOW, PALM OIL, COCONUT OIL, ESSENTIAL OILS, NATURAL CLAYS, EXFOLIATING SEEDS, MIXED HERBS</p>
					<p class="ing-extra">• SOOTHES SENSITIVE SKIN WITH EXTRACTS.</p>
					<p class="ing-extra">• RESTORES NATURAL VITALITY AND BALANCE.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="mobile-modal" id="modal-rainforest">
			<div class="modal-box">
				<button class="modal-x" data-close="modal-rainforest">✕</button>
				<h3>INGREDIENTS</h3>
				<p>NATURAL TALLOW, PALM OIL, COCONUT OIL, ESSENTIAL OILS, NATURAL CLAYS, EXFOLIATING SEEDS, MIXED HERBS</p>
				<hr/>
				<p class="bullet-item">TALLOW IS BIO-IDENTICAL TO SEBUM.</p>
				<p class="bullet-item">RICH IN VITAMINS A, D, E, AND K.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Cart Button & Panel -->
		<div class="cart-anchor">
			<button id="cart-open" class="cart-pill"><span id="cart-tally">0</span> ITEMS</button>
		</div>
		<div class="cart-shield" id="cart-shield"></div>
		<div class="cart-panel" id="cart-panel">
			<div class="cart-top">
				<h3>YOUR ORDER</h3>
				<button id="cart-exit" style="background:none;border:none;color:#888;font-size:1.4rem;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;">CLOSE ✕</button>
			</div>
			<div id="cart-body" class="cart-body">
				<p class="cart-empty">YOUR CRATE IS EMPTY</p>
			</div>
			<div class="cart-bottom">
				<div class="cart-math"><span>TOTAL</span><span id="cart-total">R0</span></div>
				<button id="wa-btn" class="checkout-btn" disabled>ORDER ON WHATSAPP</button>
			</div>
		</div>

	</main>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
// Wrapped in IIFE — runs immediately, no fragile imports
(function() {
	var cart = {};
	var qtys = { charcoal: 1, rooibos: 1, cocoa: 1, rainforest: 1 };

	function getQtyEl(pid) { return document.getElementById('qty-val-' + pid); }

	function drawCart() {
		var body = document.getElementById('cart-body');
		var tally = document.getElementById('cart-tally');
		var total = document.getElementById('cart-total');
		var wa = document.getElementById('wa-btn');
		var keys = Object.keys(cart);

		if (!body) return;

		if (keys.length === 0) {
			body.innerHTML = '<p class="cart-empty">YOUR CRATE IS EMPTY</p>';
			if (tally) tally.textContent = '0';
			if (total) total.textContent = 'R0';
			if (wa) wa.disabled = true;
			return;
		}

		var count = 0, sum = 0;
		var html = '';
		keys.forEach(function(name) {
			var qty = cart[name];
			count += qty;
			sum += qty * 100;
			html += '<div class="cart-row">' +
				'<div class="cart-row-top"><span>' + name + '</span><span>R' + (qty * 100) + '</span></div>' +
				'<div class="cart-row-btns">' +
				'<button onclick="rebelCartDec(\'' + name + '\')" class="cv-btn">-</button>' +
				'<span class="cv-val">' + qty + '</span>' +
				'<button onclick="rebelCartInc(\'' + name + '\')" class="cv-btn">+</button>' +
				'</div></div>';
		});

		body.innerHTML = html;
		if (tally) tally.textContent = count.toString();
		if (total) total.textContent = 'R' + sum;
		if (wa) wa.disabled = false;
	}

	// Expose cart helpers globally so onclick in injected HTML works
	window.rebelCartInc = function(name) { if (cart[name] !== undefined) { cart[name]++; drawCart(); } };
	window.rebelCartDec = function(name) {
		if (cart[name] !== undefined) {
			cart[name]--;
			if (cart[name] <= 0) delete cart[name];
			drawCart();
		}
	};

	document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {

		// --- QTY BUTTONS ---
		document.querySelectorAll('.qty-dec').forEach(function(btn) {
			btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
				var pid = btn.getAttribute('data-pid');
				if (!pid) return;
				if (!qtys[pid]) qtys[pid] = 1;
				if (qtys[pid] > 1) qtys[pid]--;
				var el = getQtyEl(pid);
				if (el) el.textContent = qtys[pid];
			});
		});
		document.querySelectorAll('.qty-inc').forEach(function(btn) {
			btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
				var pid = btn.getAttribute('data-pid');
				if (!pid) return;
				if (!qtys[pid]) qtys[pid] = 1;
				qtys[pid]++;
				var el = getQtyEl(pid);
				if (el) el.textContent = qtys[pid];
			});
		});

		// --- ADD TO ORDER BUTTONS ---
		document.querySelectorAll('.add-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
			btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
				var name = btn.getAttribute('data-name');
				var pid = btn.getAttribute('data-pid');
				if (!name || !pid) return;
				var q = qtys[pid] || 1;
				if (!cart[name]) cart[name] = 0;
				cart[name] += q;
				btn.classList.add('added');
				setTimeout(function() { btn.classList.remove('added'); }, 2000);
				drawCart();
			});
		});

		// --- INGREDIENTS MODALS ---
		document.querySelectorAll('.ing-open').forEach(function(btn) {
			btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
				var mid = btn.getAttribute('data-modal');
				if (mid) {
					var el = document.getElementById(mid);
					if (el) el.classList.add('open');
				}
			});
		});
		document.querySelectorAll('.modal-x').forEach(function(btn) {
			btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
				var mid = btn.getAttribute('data-close');
				if (mid) {
					var el = document.getElementById(mid);
					if (el) el.classList.remove('open');
				}
			});
		});
		// Close modal on backdrop click
		document.querySelectorAll('.mobile-modal').forEach(function(modal) {
			modal.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
				if (e.target === modal) modal.classList.remove('open');
			});
		});

		// --- CART PANEL ---
		var cartPanel = document.getElementById('cart-panel');
		var cartShield = document.getElementById('cart-shield');
		var cartOpen = document.getElementById('cart-open');
		var cartExit = document.getElementById('cart-exit');

		if (cartOpen) cartOpen.addEventListener('click', function() {
			if (cartPanel) cartPanel.classList.add('visible');
			if (cartShield) cartShield.classList.add('visible');
		});
		if (cartExit) cartExit.addEventListener('click', function() {
			if (cartPanel) cartPanel.classList.remove('visible');
			if (cartShield) cartShield.classList.remove('visible');
		});
		if (cartShield) cartShield.addEventListener('click', function() {
			if (cartPanel) cartPanel.classList.remove('visible');
			cartShield.classList.remove('visible');
		});

		// --- WHATSAPP CHECKOUT ---
		var waBtn = document.getElementById('wa-btn');
		if (waBtn) waBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
			var num = "27636936204";
			var total = 0;
			var msg = "Hi RebelCo! My soap order:\n\n";
			Object.keys(cart).forEach(function(name) {
				msg += '• ' + cart[name] + ' x ' + name + ' (R' + (cart[name] * 100) + ')\n';
				total += cart[name] * 100;
			});
			msg += '\nTOTAL: R' + total + '\n\nNo Excuses.';
			window.open('https://wa.me/' + num + '?text=' + encodeURIComponent(msg), '_blank');
		});

		// --- SMOOTH SCROLL (native, no library needed) ---
		document.documentElement.style.scrollBehavior = 'smooth';

		// --- PARALLAX ---
		window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
			var scrollY = window.scrollY;
			document.querySelectorAll('.nature-bg').forEach(function(bg) {
				bg.style.transform = 'translateY(' + (scrollY * 0.05) + 'px)';
			});
		}, { passive: true });
	});

})();
</script>

<style>
	:root { --gold: #f59e0b; }
	* { box-sizing: border-box; }
	html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #000; color: #fff; font-family: 'Staatliches', cursive; overflow-x: hidden; }

	/* ── BACKGROUNDS ─────────────────────────────────── */
	/* z-index: 1 so overflow:hidden doesn't clip it;    */
	/* pointer-events:none so it never blocks clicks     */
	.page-section {
		min-height: 100vh; width: 100vw;
		position: relative; display: flex;
		align-items: center; justify-content: center;
	}
	.nature-bg {
		position: absolute; inset: -20%;
		background-size: cover; background-position: center;
		filter: brightness(0.38) saturate(1.4);
		z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
	}
	/* All real content sits above the background */
	.section-content { position: relative; z-index: 10; width: 95%; }

	/* ── LANDING ─────────────────────────────────────── */
	.landing-content { 
		display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
		text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 2rem;
	}
	.hero-logo { width: clamp(180px, 35vw, 320px); height: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.8)); }
	.landing-tagline { font-family: 'Bangers', cursive; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem); margin: 0; text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,1); }
	.about-rebel-box {
		padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;
		background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); text-align: left;
		font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.5;
	}
	.scroll-hint { font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 0.3rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 1rem; }

	/* ── PRODUCT GRID ────────────────────────────────── */
	.product-layout {
		display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr 1fr;
		max-width: 1700px; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; padding: 3rem 0;
	}
	.main-interaction { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
	.product-pure-img { width: 100%; max-height: 48vh; object-fit: contain; filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,1)); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
	.main-title { font-family: 'Bangers', cursive; font-size: 4rem; margin: 0; text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,1); }
	.main-price { font-family: 'Bangers', cursive; font-size: 3rem; color: var(--gold); margin: 0.5rem 0; }

	/* ── CONTROLS ────────────────────────────────────── */
	.buying-tools { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: stretch; margin-top: 1.5rem; position: relative; z-index: 20; }
	.quantity-box {
		display: flex; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
		border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden;
	}
	.qty-dec, .qty-inc {
		background: none; border: none; color: #fff;
		padding: 0.8rem 1.4rem; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.8rem;
		transition: background 0.2s;
	}
	.qty-dec:hover, .qty-inc:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
	.qty-count { min-width: 55px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; }

	.add-btn {
		background: var(--gold); color: #000; border: none; padding: 0 2.5rem;
		font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer;
		border-radius: 6px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.2s;
	}
	.add-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
